=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>API 문서 자동화</h1>\n<h2 id=\"기술-스택\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%88%A0-%EC%8A%A4%ED%83%9D\" aria-label=\"기술 스택 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기술 스택</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Spring-REST-Docs</code> : API 검증 테스트, adoc 문서 빌드</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">REST-Docs-API-Spec</code> : adoc 형식을 OpenAPI3 형식으로 컨버팅</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">OpenAPI3</code> : Swagger 문서를 빌드하는 API 표준 형식</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Swagger-UI</code> : Swagger와는 달리 독립적으로 실행 가능 (npm, docker, unpkg 지원)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"workflow\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#workflow\" aria-label=\"workflow permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Workflow</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>신규 API 생성 (혹은 API 문서 신규 작성)</li>\n<li>테스팅 실시하며 <code class=\"language-text\">Spring-REST-Docs</code>로 해당 API 스펙 <code class=\"language-text\">.doc</code> 형식으로 문서화</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">.doc</code> 형식을 <code class=\"language-text\">restdocs-api-spec</code> <strong>을 이용해</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">OpenAPI3</code> <strong>형식으로 컨버팅 (</strong><code class=\"language-text\">json</code><strong>,</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">yaml</code> <strong>모두 지원)</strong></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Swagger-UI</code> 에 <code class=\"language-text\">OpenAPI3</code> 형식을 모아 빌드해서 API 문서를 완성\n<ol>\n<li>하나의 API문서만 운영하면 됨.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"응용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%91%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"응용 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>응용</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Swagger로 작성된 HLM API 문서화를 Swagger-ui를 적용하려 할 때, 지적된 문제점\n<ol>\n<li>OpenAPI3 형식의 문서를 따로 관리해야 한다.</li>\n<li>해당 형식을 호스팅해줘야 한다.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>하지만, API 문서를 모두 모아 운영할 수 있다면, 편익이 더 크다.\n<ol>\n<li>비지니스 로직에서 Swagger Annotation 관련 코드조각이 모두 빠진다.</li>\n<li>프로덕트 관련 조직과의 협업에 있어 API 문서를 url 하나로 운용할 수 있다.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>GitHub Actions에 Testing 로직을 추가한 것처럼 dev에서 호스팅하고 있는 swagger 문서처럼 붙일 수 있으면 가장 좋음.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"검토\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%80%ED%86%A0\" aria-label=\"검토 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>검토</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>코틀린으로 작성?\n<ol>\n<li>pros: best practice 많음</li>\n<li>cons: 팀 단위 학습비용 필요</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"references\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#references\" aria-label=\"references permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>References</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://rlxuc0ppd.toastcdn.net/presentation/%5BNHN%20FORWARD%202020%5DMSA%20%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%20API%20%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C%20%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://rlxuc0ppd.toastcdn.net/presentation/[NHN FORWARD 2020]MSA 환경에서 API 문서 관리하기.pdf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://taetaetae.github.io/posts/a-combination-of-swagger-and-spring-restdocs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://taetaetae.github.io/posts/a-combination-of-swagger-and-spring-restdocs/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tech.kakaoenterprise.com/127\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://tech.kakaoenterprise.com/127</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://techblog.woowahan.com/2597/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://techblog.woowahan.com/2597/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://techblog.woowahan.com/2678/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://techblog.woowahan.com/2678/</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"API 문서 자동화","summary":"1. 신규 API 생성 (혹은 API 문서 신규 작성) 2. 테스팅 실시하며 `Spring-REST-Docs`로 해당 API 스펙 `.doc` 형식으로 문서화 3. `.doc` 형식을 `restdocs-api-spec` **을 이용해** `OpenAPI3` **형식으로 컨버팅 (**`json`**,** `yaml` **모두 지원)** 4. `Swagger-UI` 에 `OpenAPI3` 형식을 모아 빌드해서 API 문서를 완성","date":"2022.05.11.","categories":["Web","documentation","API","TEST"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/784e54d13b6a44505d9e4beaf47fb48f/f0aed/test23.png","srcSet":"/static/784e54d13b6a44505d9e4beaf47fb48f/596d0/test23.png 160w,\n/static/784e54d13b6a44505d9e4beaf47fb48f/85b41/test23.png 320w,\n/static/784e54d13b6a44505d9e4beaf47fb48f/f0aed/test23.png 640w","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/784e54d13b6a44505d9e4beaf47fb48f/7ee75/test23.webp 160w,\n/static/784e54d13b6a44505d9e4beaf47fb48f/5912d/test23.webp 320w,\n/static/784e54d13b6a44505d9e4beaf47fb48f/264e0/test23.webp 640w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"}]},"width":640,"height":334}},"publicURL":"/static/784e54d13b6a44505d9e4beaf47fb48f/test23.png"}},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#api-%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C-%EC%9E%90%EB%8F%99%ED%99%94\">API 문서 자동화</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%88%A0-%EC%8A%A4%ED%83%9D\">기술 스택</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#workflow\">Workflow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%9D%91%EC%9A%A9\">응용</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B2%80%ED%86%A0\">검토</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#references\">References</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/api/"}},
